# Personal ditto data — style profile, post history, keys.
# These normally live in ~/.claude/ditto/ (outside this repo); the rules
# below are a safety net in case a file ends up inside the plugin tree.
profile.md
history.md
**/ditto/**/profile.md
**/ditto/**/history.md
.env
*.local

# Windows / stray artifacts
nul
Thumbs.db
